
AHF: Apparent Horizon Finder
============================
JG 3/2007, based on AHfinder


To compile:
----------

In MyConfig:

Comment out the line

projects += src/projects/AHfinder

and add the line (BB: after projects/Gauge !) 

projects += src/projects/AHF

then: make new


